formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. SBI, Info City branch Gandhinagar has sanctioned loan of Rs. 47 Cr. for the Project i.e. Siddhraj Z2 vide sanction letter number MERM/R-1/19-20/365 dt. 17-09-2019 and created mortgage deed dt. 31-12-2019. An additional amount of Rs. 20211000 was sanctioned for the project Siddhraj Z2 vide sanction letter number NIL dt. NIL at the time of Covid 19 pandemic.
2. S V Realty has been disbursed an amount of Rs. 40,00,00,000  for the said project till the date of this certificate from the first loan. Out of this loan a repayment of Rs. 25,48,00,931 has been done till the date of this certificate. In addition to this, an amount of Rs. 2,02,00,000  pre approved loan facility Guaranteed Emergency Credit Line (GECL) offer letter, was disbursed for the Siddhraj Z2 project till date of this certificate. Out of this total repayment of Rs. 1,21,67,302 has been done for GECL loan till the date of this certificate.

3. The total cost of construction has increased the estimated cost to complete the project. The overrun is of Rs. 21,80,61,459 till the date of this certificate.
